            "body": "lua53+ have \"math.maxinteger\" https://github.com/lua/lua/blob/37a1b72706b6e55e60b8d73bcbe269921976825e/lmathlib.c#L743-L748\n\nI see lua53 compat is used in this repo, but the lua module seems not imported. (only c-api is used, it seems a dependencies of luv https://github.com/luvit/luv/pull/279)\n\nbut the way how it get a maxinteger is a pure lua impl, interesting.\nhttps://github.com/lunarmodules/lua-compat-5.3/blob/4f445bfaf6d970d7df1479b960fa4f2bac63047c/compat53/module.lua#L106-L119",
